snippet.title: Kamikaze for the Apple II
snippet.description:
Came also out for:

---


Game description:

Kamikaze is an arcade-style action game, where you, as an anti-air ship destroy hostile planes, which try to destroy you.

If you reach over 500 points, sea mines will also appear.


What I think:

Challenging game, that gets repetitive rather quite quickly.


NOTE:

The picture at the beginiing is NOT the cover. I couldn't find it (and maybe there is not even one), and I found this of a contest, so I used this, because I liked it.
